<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Community Support</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/communitySupport.css">
</head>
<body>

  <section class="community-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Community Support</h1>
      <p class="head">Farmers face significant challenges in accessing markets, often resulting in lower income due to dependence on middlemen. Our goal is to build a strong community of farmers, consumers, and retailers to reduce this gap and improve their income potential.</p>

      <div class="support-info">
        <div class="info-box">
          <h2>How You Can Help</h2>
          <p>By joining our platform, you can support farmers in showcasing their products directly to consumers and retailers. As a buyer, you can purchase fresh produce while ensuring fair prices for farmers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box">
          <h2>For Farmers</h2>
          <p>We encourage farmers to sign up and list their produce on the platform. This way, you can connect directly with buyers, negotiate fair prices, and manage your transactions easily without relying on intermediaries.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box">
          <h2>For Consumers & Retailers</h2>
          <p>Consumers and retailers can help by buying produce directly from farmers. This not only ensures fresh products but also strengthens the local farming community by providing fair prices and transparent transactions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cta">
        <a href="#" class="join-btn">Join the Community</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
